@context: Expand Testing Gauntlet - A comprehensive playground covering authentication, form inputs, checkboxes, radio buttons, dropdowns, and dynamic tables.
@blueprint: multi_page_feature_validation

# 🐾 EXPAND TESTING GAUNTLET: The Ultimate Playground

1. NAVIGATE to https://practice.expandtesting.com/login
2. Fill 'Username' field with 'practice'
3. Fill 'Password' field with 'SuperSecretPassword!'
4. Click the 'Login' button
5. VERIFY that 'You logged into a secure area!' is present.

6. NAVIGATE to https://practice.expandtesting.com/inputs
7. Fill 'Input Number' field with '4242'
8. Fill 'Input Text' field with 'Cyber Manul'
9. Fill 'Input Password' field with 'ManulSecret'
10. Fill 'Input Date' field with '12/31/2026'
11. Click the 'Display Inputs' button
12. VERIFY that 'Cyber Manul' is present.
13. VERIFY that '4242' is present.

14. NAVIGATE to https://practice.expandtesting.com/checkboxes
15. Check the checkbox for 'Checkbox 1'
16. Uncheck the checkbox for 'Checkbox 2'
17. VERIFY that 'Checkbox 1' is checked.
18. VERIFY that 'Checkbox 2' is not checked.

19. NAVIGATE to https://practice.expandtesting.com/radio-buttons
20. Click the radio button for 'Black'
21. VERIFY that 'Black' is checked.
22. Click the radio button for 'Basketball'
23. VERIFY that 'Basketball' is checked.

24. NAVIGATE to https://practice.expandtesting.com/dropdown
25. Select 'Option 2' from the 'Simple dropdown' list
26. VERIFY that 'Option 2' is present.
27. Select '100' from the 'Elements per page' dropdown

28. NAVIGATE to https://practice.expandtesting.com/dynamic-table
29. EXTRACT the CPU of 'Chrome' into {chrome_cpu}
30. EXTRACT the Memory of 'Firefox' into {firefox_memory}
31. EXTRACT the Network of 'Internet Explorer' into {internet_explorer_network}

32. DONE.